OL,6,     FThe competition kicks off at The
OL,7,     FUnicorn Inn in Ludlow, where Zoe
OL,8,     Fand Lee hope that their glamorous,
OL,9,     Ffairy-tale rooms will become the
OL,10,     Fstuff of legend. And Zoe wows the
OL,11,     Fguests at breakfast.
